National Salvation Association of Cinema. When Ko makes a uproar at the dance parlour and rips apart his friend's zombie costume, it represents Cai's criticism on the muddling-along attitude of Hong Kong society at the time. The characters' decision to return to the mainland to join the resistance effort also foretells Cai's decision to do the same in real-life.","poster_path":"/viNjBOPJ3PgFyCZyrksoUEo84S0.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"zh","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":0.1788,"release_date":"1941-01-01","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0}]},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":4393748,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zhang Gang","original_name":"Zhang Gang","popularity":0.0214,"profile_path":"/2eofXJo2UrC8cVnvzHkCAH3tipn.jpg","known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/wfQ5y0vS9Cd4hK03Mhiza9Vry2N.jpg","id":195648,"name":"CCTV Spring Festival Gala: Crosstalk and Sketch","original_name":"央视春晚相声小品","overview":"","poster_path":"/i61poXdAvfQ454cLOV4qdrissOF.jpg","media_type":"tv","original_language":"zh","genre_ids":[10764,10767],"popularity":21.6954,"first_air_date":"1983-02-12","softcore":false,"vote_average":9.0,"vote_count":1,"origin_country":["CN"]}]},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2097506,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zhang Yong Gang","original_name":"Zhang Yong Gang","popularity":0.0398,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/ram3d2fu3nmc6yI4jB7y48ysTH.jpg","id":106617,"name":"Heroes","original_name":"大侠霍元甲","overview":"The Refornment Movement of 1898 resulted in the \"Six Heroes\" dying. Huo Yuan Jia, who was filled with patriotic enthusiasm, had been eager to participate; however, he fell into the enemy's trap and could only watch as the heroes of the country died. Not long after, China was invaded by the enemy.\n\nA year later, Huo Yuan Jia who was now living in ChangZhou took a stroll along the mountainside. Discouraged by his past and in fear of falling into the enemy'